# 📚 Street Bites API - Complete Routes Reference

## 🔐 Authentication Required
**Header:** `Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>`

---

## 1️⃣ Authentication Routes (`/api/auth`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| POST | `/register` | Public | নতুন user registration |
| POST | `/login` | Public | User login |
| POST | `/refresh-token` | Public | Token refresh |
| GET | `/profile` | Protected | User profile দেখুন |
| PUT | `/profile` | Protected | Profile update |
| POST | `/change-password` | Protected | Password পরিবর্তন |
| POST | `/logout` | Protected | Logout |
| POST | `/forgot-password` | Public | Password reset request |
| POST | `/reset-password` | Public | Reset password |

