### Success Response
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "অপারেশন সফল হয়েছে",
  "data": {
    // Response data here
  }
}
```

### Error Response
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Error message in Bangla",
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "details": "Detailed error message"
  }
}
```

