## 🔐 Authorization Roles

| Role | Access Level | Description |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| **Owner** | Full Access | সব endpoints access করতে পারে |
| **Employee** | Limited | Stall management, Order processing |
| **Customer** | Basic | Order করা, Profile manage |
| **Investor** | Read-only | Reports এবং analytics দেখা |

---

